text: Marlyse Hourtou is an archer from Chad. She was born on 29 July 1996 in N'Djamena. Hourtou competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Marlyse HourtouMarlyse HOURTOU == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Chadian people Category:Archers Category:Olympians
